00:03:31.590 --> 00:03:33.235
Let's talk for a moment

00:03:33.259 --> 00:03:36.927
about what it means to be in jail
even for a few days.

00:03:37.368 --> 00:03:40.345
Well, it can mean losing your job,

00:03:40.369 --> 00:03:41.702
losing your home,

00:03:41.726 --> 00:03:43.793
jeopardizing your immigration status.

00:03:44.169 --> 00:03:46.943
It may even mean
losing custody of your children.

00:03:47.598 --> 00:03:50.281
A third of sexual
victimization by jail staff

00:03:50.305 --> 00:03:53.076
happens in the first three days in jail,

00:03:53.100 --> 00:03:57.335
and almost half of all jail deaths,
including suicides,

00:03:57.359 --> 00:03:59.166
happen in that first week.

